OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F335A1784305119
OL,3,CDeath of 'gentle giant' restrained in
OL,4,Cjewellers not unlawful
OL,6,FThe death of a "gentle giant" who was
OL,7,Frestrained following an altercation
OL,8,Fwith a jewellery shop security guard
OL,9,Fwas not unlawful, a coroner has found.
OL,11,FSam Diatta, 39, went into cardiac
OL,12,Farrest while being held on the floor
OL,13,Fof Mappin and Webb jewellers in York
OL,14,Fon 26 July 2022.
OL,26,@nD@POUnD@]O]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,336,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F335A1784305119
OL,3,CDeath of 'gentle giant' restrained in
OL,4,Cjewellers not unlawful
OL,6,FAn inquest heard Mr Diatta, who had
OL,7,Fbipolar disorder, was suffering an
OL,8,Facute mental health episode when he
OL,9,Ftold shop security guard Gary Prothero
OL,10,Fhe wanted to take pictures of watches
OL,11,Ffor his 18,000 TikTok followers in
OL,12,Freturn for free watches.
OL,14,FWhen Mr Prothero asked him to leave,
OL,15,Fhe threw several punches at him,
OL,16,Fbefore a customer intervened.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,336,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F335A1784305119
OL,3,CDeath of 'gentle giant' restrained in
OL,4,Cjewellers not unlawful
OL,6,FCCTV footage showed Mr Diatta being
OL,7,Ftackled to the floor. Two more members
OL,8,Fof the public came to help, meaning he
OL,9,Fwas being held down by four men when
OL,10,Fpolice arrived.
OL,12,FTwo pathologists said that the medical
OL,13,Fcause of death was hypertensive heart
OL,14,Fdisease, combined with the effects of
OL,15,Fbeing restrained. One said the
OL,16,Frestraint would have reduced Mr
OL,17,FDiatta's breathing.
OL,19,FAfter Mr Diatta's death, police
OL,20,Farrested four men ` but later said no-
OL,21,Fone would face any charges.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,336,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F335A1784305119
OL,3,CDeath of 'gentle giant' restrained in
OL,4,Cjewellers not unlawful
OL,6,FOn Thursday, coroner Jon Heath said Mr
OL,7,FDiatta's family had asked him to
OL,8,Fconsider that the "disproportionate
OL,9,Fuse of restraint was an unlawful act"
OL,10,Fas it was "dangerous and likely to
OL,11,Fcause injury".
OL,13,FBut Mr Heath said none of the four men
OL,14,Fknew of Mr Diatta's mental health
OL,15,Fissues or heart condition, and did not
OL,16,Fbelieve he was struggling to breathe.
OL,18,FThe coroner said Mr Prothero had been
OL,19,Fhit in the face and was acting in self-
OL,20,Fdefence when he initially restrained
OL,21,FMr Diatta.
OL,26,@pD@SOUqD@eO]rD@KOUsD@MO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,336,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F335A1784305119
OL,3,CDeath of 'gentle giant' restrained in
OL,4,Cjewellers not unlawful
OL,6,FHe said the other men involved thought
OL,7,Fthere had been a robbery, and all of
OL,8,Fthem were restraining Mr Diatta
OL,9,Fbecause the police had been called.
OL,11,FMr Heath concluded that Mr Diatta's
OL,12,Fdeath did not amount to manslaughter,
OL,13,Fand was not an unlawful killing.
OL,15,FHe recorded a narrative conclusion
OL,16,Fthat Mr Diatta died as a consequence
OL,17,Fof naturally occurring heart disease
OL,18,Fcombined with the effects of being
OL,19,Frestrained.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,336,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F335A1784305119
OL,3,CDeath of 'gentle giant' restrained in
OL,4,Cjewellers not unlawful
OL,6,FThe inquest heard that Mr Diatta had
OL,7,Fbeen discharged from a psychiatric
OL,8,Fhospital four days before his death,
OL,9,Fand his family said they believed he
OL,10,Fwas not well enough to be living in
OL,11,Fthe community at the time.
OL,13,FIn a statement read after the hearing
OL,14,Fby their barrister Parissa Najah, Mr
OL,15,FDiatta's parents George and Judy, and
OL,16,Fhis sister Teba, said: "On the fateful
OL,17,Fday of Sam's death he was suffering an
OL,18,Facute mental health episode.
OL,26,@xD@XOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,336,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F335A1784305119
OL,3,CDeath of 'gentle giant' restrained in
OL,4,Cjewellers not unlawful
OL,6,F"He was restrained, face down on the
OL,7,Ffloor for more than seven minutes,
OL,8,Fduring which time he shouted: 'I can't
OL,9,Fbreathe'. Tragically, those words were
OL,10,Fnot heeded.
OL,12,F"Being restrained in that position,
OL,13,Ffor so long, by several men was
OL,14,Festablished by the coroner as being
OL,15,Fpart of the medical cause of Sam's
OL,16,Fdeath.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,336,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F335A1784305119
OL,3,CDeath of 'gentle giant' restrained in
OL,4,Cjewellers not unlawful
OL,6,F"The family remain convinced that Stan
OL,7,Fwas not well enough to be living in
OL,8,Fthe community in the days prior to his
OL,9,Fdeath, due to the concerns about his
OL,10,Fmental health and how it had
OL,11,Fdeteriorated.
OL,13,F"Their view is reinforced by the fact
OL,14,Fthat, just four days after his
OL,15,Fdischarge from hospital, Sam lost his
OL,16,Flife in circumstances that could have
OL,17,Fbeen avoided."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUyD@NO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,336,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F335A1784305119
OL,3,CDeath of 'gentle giant' restrained in
OL,4,Cjewellers not unlawful
OL,6,FTeba Diatta said: "Sam wasn't a bad
OL,7,Fperson. He was having a really bad day
OL,8,Fdue to his mental health, and he was a
OL,9,Flovely, gentle soul.
OL,11,F"He was very forgiving. He was kind,
OL,12,Fhe was loving, he was generous. We
OL,13,Freally miss him. And we just don't
OL,14,Fwant him to be remembered for an act
OL,15,Fof violence on a day that he was so
OL,16,Fpoorly."
OL,18,FShe added: "We choose forgiveness, we
OL,19,Fdon't want to hold it against any of
OL,20,Fthe people involved."
OL,26,@nD@SOUsD@AOUxD@HO]zD@LOU|D@UO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,336,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F335A1784305119
OL,3,CDeath of 'gentle giant' restrained in
OL,4,Cjewellers not unlawful
OL,6,FThe family said when Mr Diatta was 20,
OL,7,Fhe jumped into the River Ouse to save
OL,8,Fa woman who was trying to kill
OL,9,Fherself, and that heroic act was
OL,10,F"typically him".
OL,12,FAfter his death, Mr Diatta's family
OL,13,Fsaid he was "a gentle giant, who was
OL,14,Fkind and generous and loved by all who
OL,15,Fmet him".
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@OO]uD@MOUwD@HO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G10/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,336,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F335A1784305119
OL,3,CDeath of 'gentle giant' restrained in
OL,4,Cjewellers not unlawful
OL,6,FThey said: "Sam was half Senegalese
OL,7,Fand his family in Senegal meant the
OL,8,Fworld to him. He was a keen sportsman
OL,9,Fand supported both the England and
OL,10,FSenegal football sides. He also played
OL,11,Ffor York RI rugby team.
OL,13,F"Sadly, in his later teenage years Sam
OL,14,Fdeveloped mental health issues which
OL,15,Fstayed with him throughout his life.
OL,17,F"He had a strong Christian faith and
OL,18,Fwith two others led the Christian
OL,19,FUnion at York College."
OL,26,@nD@LOUuD@AOUyD@AOU{D@WO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G11/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
